<item>
            <title>[SOLR-8567] SOLR-839 broke the Maven build (trunk, 5.5)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8567</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-839&quot; title=&quot;XML Query Parser support (deftype=xmlparser)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-839&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-839&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; adds a new code dependency between the Solr test code and the Lucene test code.  ant handles this with some updates to the common-build.xml (included in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-839&quot; title=&quot;XML Query Parser support (deftype=xmlparser)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-839&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-839&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;) but the maven build mechanism needs updates to the pom.xml.template with an equivalent change.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
